""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" function f keys :-
"""""""""""""""""

" f1 is help in gnome terminal and hard to use.

" f2 = (echo) show current file name
nnoremap <f2>     :echo @%<cr>

" <f3><f3> show me the buffer list :-
nnoremap <F3><f3> :buffers<cr>:b<Space>
" <f3> switch buffers :-
nnoremap <f3>     :b #<cr>

""""""""""""""""""
