"""""""""""""""""""""

" <Leader>a is used by perlstacktrace "add" point.

nnoremap <Leader>b :echo "leader b unused"<cr>

nnoremap <Leader>c :echo "leader c unused"<cr>

""""" YUCK ! " map <Leader>ca :%s/^/#/g<cr>:%s/^#\+/#/g<cr>

